title: Storytime: Saving a Little Girls Life While Apartment Hunting/Confronting Some Haters in Spanish
description:
This episode is a whirlwind of chaos, story times and celebrity gossip. Camo has been hunting for their first apartment on their own, on their way out of a tour they saved a little girl's life. Tune in for all the tea on that and a confrontation between Camo and some haters at the spa. 
For 50% off your first Care/of order, go to https://TakeCareOf.com and enter code unfazed50.
